<div class="postmsg">
<p>Ok, i just figure out other way to make tha background fix my monitors. <br/>What I did just in case if someone faces the same problem, I set to all my monitors as background the image I wanted as login background, after that I take a screenshot of all my monitors. The screenshot looks similar to this <br/><span class="postimg"><img src="https://s20.postimg.org/qxzp9oegd/background.png" alt="background.png"/></span></p><p>And set this one as login background. <br/>That was all and everything fits well now</p>
